IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: TO CONNECT ENTREPRENEURIAL COMPANIES WITH HIGH VALUE RESOURCES TO ACCELERATE BUSINESS GROWTH.
IRS990.MissionDesc: TO CONNECT ENTREPRENEURIAL COMPANIES WITH HIGH-VALUE RESOURECES SUCH AS EDUCATION, MENTORING AND CAPITAL CONNECTIONS/FORMATION, TO ACCELERATE BUSINESS GROWTH.
IRS990.Desc: CED OPERATES ITS NON-PROFIT PROGRAMS ACCORDING TO A STRATEGIC VISION ADOPTED BY THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS.PROGRAMS LIKE GRO INCUBATOR PROVIDE EDUCATION FOR EARLY STAGE COMPANIES AND FOUNDERS. THE CURRICULUM IS SUPPORTED BY SUCCESSFUL FOUNDERS WHO PROVIDE EXPERTISE AND ADVICE FOR SCALE.VENTURE CONNECT IS ANOTHER PROGRAM THAT ENABLES STARTUP COMPANIES TO CONNECT TO THE RESOURCES THEY NEED TO GROW. THIS IS THE CULMINATION OF YEAR-ROUND PROGRESS ACHIEVED THROUGH SUPPORT/GUIDANCE OFFERED BY CED TEAM DIRECTLY TO STARTUPS.THE ANNUAL CONFERENCE (VENTURE CONNECT) RETURNED TO IN-PERSON FORMAT IN 2022. THE EVENT HOSTS OVER 800 PP AND PROVIDES EDUCATION, CONNECTIONS AND NETWORKING OPPORTUNITIES.CED ENGAGES OVER 400 PARTNERS IN THE BUSINESS COMMUNITY INCLUDING STARTUPS, CORPORATE, INVESTORS, AND OTHER INDIVIDUALS. CED LAUNCHED A SUPPORT ORGANIZATION NETWORK INTENDED TO BRING TOGETHER ENTITIES SUPPORTING ENTREPRENEURS TO FOSTER COLLABORATION ACROSS THE ECOSYSTEM.CED CONTINUES TO MAINTAIN PARTNERSHIPS WITH EDUCATIONAL INSTITUTIONS HELPING TO SUPPORT BUSINESS DEVELOPMENT AND ECONOMIC GROWTH.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: IT IS CED'S POLICY TO EVALUATE ALL TAX POSITIONS TO IDENTIFY ANY THAT MAY BE CONSIDERED UNCERTAIN. ALL IDENTIFIED MATERIAL TAX POSITIONS ARE ASSESSED AND MEASURED BY A "MORE-LIKELY-THAN-NOT" THRESHOLD TO DETERMINE IF THE TAX POSITION IS UNCERTAIN AND WHAT, IF ANY, THE EFFECT OF THE UNCERTAIN TAX POSITION MAY HAVE ON THE FINANCIAL STATEMENTS. NO MATERIAL UNCERTAIN TAX POSITIONS WERE IDENTIFIED FOR 2023 OR 2022.
THE EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE, WHICH SERVES AS A SUBCOMMITTEE OF THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS, REVIEWS ALL MATTERS RELATED TO COMPENSATION AND POLICIES OF THE EMPLOYEES OF THE ORGANIZATION.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 11B
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE FINANCE COMMITTEE DOES A DETAILED REVIEW AND REPORTS TO THE EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE AND BOARD. A DRAFT COPY OF THE ORGANIZATION'S 990 IS AVAILABLE TO THE EXECUTIVE COMMITTEE AND BOARD MEMBERS PRIOR TO FILING.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 12C
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: ANNUALLY EACH EMPLOYEE AND BOARD MEMBER IS REQUIRED TO ACKNOWLEDGE THE ORGANIZATION'S POLICY BY SIGNING AND DISCLOSING (IF ANY) ALL POTENTIAL CONFLICTS OF INTEREST. INTERNALLY, EACH VENDOR THAT THE ORGANIZATION ENGAGES IS REVIEWED FOR CONFLICT OF INTEREST.
